lines.text: Who goes there friend or foe?
You're with the seven dwarfs? That's what I want to know

[singing]
We're in the army now!, we're not behind the plow!

[singing]
It takes us cats to catch them rats, we're in the army now!

[singing]
Well look who's in the suits and the suits share the zoots, and wacky off the khaki now!
De gal! And de prince! Wotta sickenin' sight!
Hello, Murder Incorporated? BLACK OUT SO WHITE!
Man, what you got dat made So White think you so hot?
Well, dat is a military secret!

[injects poison into the apple]
This will make So White weak in the knees!

[coughing]
Man that stuff smells like limburger cheese!

[examining the unconscious So White]
She's out of this world!, she's stiff as wood!, she's got it bad and that ain't good!
There's only one thing that'll remedy this and that's Prince Chawmin and his dynamite kiss!
